<< /A 9400 0 R /ActualText (Line graph showing the overall migration timing of PIT-tagged wild spring/summer chinook salmon smolts from Idaho at Lower Granite Dam in 2002, with associated river flows and spill at the dam. Data represents detections from nine Idaho streams pooled in 3-day intervales and expanded based on daily detection probability. River flows and spill at the dam were averaged daily over the same periods.) /Alt (Line graph showing the overall migration timing of PIT-tagged wild spring/summer chinook salmon smolts from Idaho at Lower Granite Dam in 2002, with associated river flows and spill at the dam. Data represents detections from nine Idaho streams pooled in 3-day intervales and expanded based on daily detection probability. River flows and spill at the dam were averaged daily over the same periods.) /K 0 /P 9394 0 R /Pg 268 0 R /S /Figure /T () >>
